OMV Petrom SA (SNP) ’s shareholders
approved the payout of about 1.8 billion lei in dividends from
the 2011 profit, or 0.031 lei per share, and the oil company’s
2012 budget plan in a general meeting, according to a statement
sent today to the Bucharest Stock Exchange.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
